author: stsp
msg: Fix incremental hotcopy of revprops belonging to packed shards.
(hotcopy_copy_packed_shard): Copy all revprops corresponding to the pack,
not just the first one. The revprop loop counter wasn't actually used
and instead the first revprop of the pack was copied multiple times...
Use the correct revision number range while copying revprops and update
that source and destination have the same idea of min-unpacked-rev
